title: Koduah nets 2 goals in Windsor victory
text:
Koduah nets 2 goals in Windsor victory By Journal Inquirer Staff Journal Inquirer | 0 comments 
Opponents have had their way with the Weaver High boys soccer team this season, and Windsor was no exception. 
Jordan Koduah had goals in each half to lead Windsor (3-8) to a 4-0 Central Conference victory over visiting Weaver (0-12) on Friday.
